In the Controller
-----------------
Install java into
/opt/jdk-x.x.x

apt-get install subversion

Unarchive tropos agent into /opt
/opt/wso2tropos-agent-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT

PHP cartridge
-------------

Add image id to repository/conf/php-cartridge-config.properties

In autoscaler
-------------
cd into binary root

rm -rf tmp
rm -rf tmpPayload
Make sure
resources/Payload file is uptodate

